This project contains material derived from the Firebird database project
(https://firebird.org), used under the Initial Developer's Public License
Version 1.0 (IDPL) and the InterBase Public License Version 1.0 (IPL):

- packages/core/src/protocol/messages.json
  Error-message templates (gds code -> message text, 2539 entries) generated
  from the Firebird source tree by scripts/generate-messages.mjs.
  Copyright (c) Firebird Project and contributors.

- packages/core/src/types/timezones.ts
  Time-zone id table derived from Firebird's src/common/TimeZones.h
  (zone identifiers from the IANA tz database, ordering fixed by the
  Firebird project). Copyright (c) Firebird Project and contributors.

The IDPL and IPL are available at:
https://www.firebirdsql.org/en/initial-developer-s-public-license-version-1-0/
https://www.firebirdsql.org/en/interbase-public-license-version-1-0/

The Firebird wire protocol implementation in this project is an independent,
clean-room-style reimplementation in TypeScript informed by the publicly
available Firebird sources and documentation; no Firebird C++ source code is
included in this package's runtime beyond the generated data files listed
above.
